snippet.title: Sniper: Ghost Warrior Contracts - Official Trailer
snippet.description: Get a look at the latest trailer for the upcoming first-person shooter and take a peek at some new features including dismemberment. The game will be released on November 22, 2019 for PlayStation 4, Xbox One, and PC.
